rabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010997, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Glory be to one, who is illuminated by power and strength. Glory be to one, who is veiled in the seven skies, so no eye sees Him. Glory be to one, who degraded the creatures through death and exalted His self by life. Glory be to one, who saves and annihilates all the things, except Himself.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Paak hai Woh zaat jisne apni quwwat o qudrat ke saath jahan ko munawwar kiya. Paak hai Woh zaat jo saath aasmaano mein makhfee hai aur is tarah se keh koi aankh usko nahi dekh sakti. Paak hai Woh zaat jisne bando’n ko maut ke saath zaleel kiya aur khud ko zindah o jaawid ki sifat se azeez o giraami banaaya. Paak hai Woh zaat hamesha zindah rahegi aur baqiyah (baaqi) sab-kuchh fana ho jaayega.", "Urdu": "پاک ہے وہ ذات جس نے اپنی قوت و قدرت کے ساتھ جہاں کو منور کیا۔ پاک ہے وہ ذات جو سات آسمانوں میں مخفی ہے اور اس طرف سے کہ کوئی آنکھ اس کو نہیں دیکھ سکتی۔ پاک ہے وہ ذات جس نے بندوں کو موت کے ساتھ ذلیل کیا اور خود کو زندہ جاوید کی صفت سے عزیز و گرامی بنایا۔ پاک ہے وہ ذات جو ہمیشہ زندہ رہے گی اور بقیہ سب کچھ فنا ہوجائے گا۔", "RArabic": "SUBHAANA MANIS TANAARA BIL-HAWLE WAL QUWWATE, SUBHAANA MANEH TAJABA FEE SAB-E’ SAMAAWAATEIN, FALAA A’YNO TARAAHO, SUBHAANA MAN AZALLAL KHALAAEQA BIL-MAWLTE, WA A-A’ZZA NAFSAHU BIL-HAYAATE, SUBHAANA MAN YABQAA WA YAFNAA KULLO SHAY-IN SEWAAHO.", "ArabicText1": "سُبْحَانَ مَنِ اسْتَنَارَ بِالْحَوْلِ وَالْقُوَّۃِ، سُبْحَانَ مَنِ احْتَجَبَ فِیْ سَبْعِ سَمَاوَاتٍ، فَلَا عَیْنُ تَرَاهُ، سُبْحَانَ مَنْ اَذَلَّ الْخَلَائِقِ بِالْمَوْتِ، وَاَعَزَّ نَفْسَهٗ بَالْحَیَاۃِ، سُبْحَانَ مَنْ یَبْقٰی وَیَفْنٰی كُلُّ شَیْءٍ سِوَاهُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010998, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Glory be to one, who reserved the praise for Himself, and chose. Glory be to the living and the knowing; Glory be to forbearing and noble; Glory be to the king and the sanctified; Glory be to the high and the great. Glory be to Allah and praise be for Him.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Paak hai Woh zaat jisne hamd o sataaish ko apne saath makhsoos qaraar diya aur us par raazi hai. Paak hai Woh zaat jo zindah aur daana hai. Paak hai Woh zaat jo burdbaar aur buzurg-waar hai. Paak hai Woh zaat jo haqeeqi baadshah aur buraaiyo’n se mubarra (alag) hai. Paak hai Woh zaat jo buzurg o bartar hai. Paak hai Woh zaat keh hamd o sataaish Usi ke saath makhsoos hai.", "Urdu": "پاک ہے وہ ذات جس نے حمد و ستائش کو اپنے ساتھ مخصوص قرار دیا۔ اور اس پر راضی ہے۔ پاک ہے وہ ذات جو زندہ اور دانا ہے۔ پاک ہے وہ ذات جو بردباد اور بزرگوار ہے۔ پاک ہے وہ ذات جو حقیقی بادشاہ اور برائیوں سے مبرا ہے۔ پاک ہے وہ ذات جو بزرگ و برتر ہے۔ پاک ہے وہ ذات کہ حمد و ستائش اسی کے ساتھ مخصوص ہے۔", "RArabic": "SUBHAANA MANIS TAKHLASAL HAMDA LE-NAFSEHI, WAR TAZAAHO, SUBHAANAL HAYYIL A’LEEME, SUBHAANAL HALEEMIL KAREEME, SUBHAANAL MALEKIL QUDDOOSE, SUBHAANAL (A’LIYYIL) A’ZEEME, SUBHAANAL LAALE WA BE-HAMDEHI.", "ArabicText1": "سُبْحَانَ مَنِ اسْتَخْلَصَ الْحَمْدَ لِنَفْسِهٖ وَارْتَضَاهُ، سُبْحَانَ الْحَیِّ الْعَلِیْمِ، سُبْحَانَ الْحَلِیْمِ الْكَرِیْمِ، سُبْحَانَ الْمَلِكِ الْقُدُّوْسِ، سُبْحَانَ (الْعَلِیِّ) الْعَظِیْمِ، سُبْحَانَ اللهِ وَبِحَمْدِهٖ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "